des:
Forget those old, boring, buzz and jingle alarms! Wake up to the old-school, analog, mechanical goodness of antique, wind-up, brass alarm clocks!

Antique Clock Alarm features 2 free antique alarms: "Wind Me Up," and "Fire Station," plus a special get-out-of-bed snooze alarm: "Victorian Door Bell."

Get Antique Alarm Gold to unlock seven MORE antique alarms including: "Little Dingbat," "Springs N' Dings," "Old Clanger," "Tinkle Toes," "Bedside Bully," "Gold Rush," and "Hell's Bells."

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you enjoyed Antique Clock Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
